libbsd (0.0.1-2) unstable; urgency=low

  * Switch to debhelper compatibility level 7.
  * Use dh_prep instead of “dh_clean -k”.
  * Add a symbols file for libbsd0.
  * Use UTF-8 copyright symbol in debian/copyright.

